RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: LBTMS_STP_MARK_PROCESS_MASTER.TRANCHE_REF_NO = LBTMS_STP_MARK_PROCESS_DETAIL.TRANCHE_REF_NO AND LBTMS_STP_MARK_PROCESS_MASTER.PARTICIPANT = LBTMS_STP_MARK_PROCESS_DETAIL.PARTICIPANT AND LBTMS_STP_MARK_PROCESS_MASTER.SEQ_NO = LBTMS_STP_MARK_PROCESS_DETAIL.SEQ_NO

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT A.BORR_REF_NO , C.FACILITY_NAME FROM LBTB_STP_INTERFACE_BROWSER A, OLTBS_CONTRACT B, OLTB_CONTRACT_MASTER C where B.MODULE_CODE = 'LB' AND B.CONTRACT_STATUS NOT IN ('L', 'V') AND A.BORR_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND B.CONTRACT_REF_NO = C.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND B.BRANCH = global.current_branch AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM smvws_user_branches b WHERE b.User_id = global.user_id AND b.Branch_code = global.current_branch) ORDER BY A.BORR_REF_NO

SELECT DISTINCT A.COUNTERPARTY , C.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM LBTBS_PART_PROC_STAT A, OLTBS_CONTRACT B, OLTMS_CUSTOMER C, LBTB_STP_INTERFACE_BROWSER D WHERE A.BORROWER_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.COUNTERPARTY = C.CUSTOMER_NO AND A.COUNTERPARTY = D.PARTICIPANT AND A.BORROWER_REF_NO = ?
